Hm), it's okay. The addendum is nicely written, with solid, believable dialogue.

You might like to use this image code instead:

+block

–block


[[includecomponent:image-block name=THE NAME OF YOUR IMAGE FILE|

IMAGE ]]




The one you're using now is kind of antiquated.

Also, I noticed a small issue with the verb tenses at the very end of your addendum.



SCP-3907-1 and SCP-3907-3 through -5 stand and raise their glasses.
附加记录：    



SCP-3907-6 jumped over the table as the entities finished the toast. SCP-3907 returned to its inactive state.
附加记录：    

First is present tense, second is past tense. I'd recommend making them both the same as the writing feels kind of disjointed otherwise.





